<refsect1 id="GdictDefbox.description" role="desc">
<title role="desc.title">Description</title>
<para>
The <link linkend="GdictDefbox"><type>GdictDefbox</type></link> widget is a composite widget showing the list of
definitions for a word. It queries the passed <link linkend="GdictContext"><type>GdictContext</type></link> and displays
the list of <link linkend="GdictDefinition"><type>GdictDefinition</type></link><!-- -->s obtained.
</para>
<para>
It provides syntax highlighting, clickable links and an embedded find
bar.</para>
<para>
</para>
</refsect1>

