<indexterm zone="gdict-defbox-jump-to-definition" role="0.1"><primary sortas="gdict_defbox_jump_to_definition">gdict_defbox_jump_to_definition</primary></indexterm><programlisting><link linkend="void">void</link>                gdict_defbox_jump_to_definition     (<link linkend="GdictDefbox">GdictDefbox</link> *defbox,
                                                         <link linkend="gint">gint</link> number);</programlisting>
<para>
Scrolls to the definition identified by <parameter>number</parameter>.  If <parameter>number</parameter> is -1,
jumps to the last definition.</para>
<para>
</para><variablelist role="params">
<varlistentry><term><parameter>defbox</parameter>&#160;:</term>
<listitem><simpara> a <link linkend="GdictDefbox"><type>GdictDefbox</type></link>
</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
<varlistentry><term><parameter>number</parameter>&#160;:</term>
<listitem><simpara> the definition to jump to
</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
</variablelist><para role="since">Since 0.1</para></refsect2>
