<refsect2 id="gdict-defbox-set-font-name" role="function" condition="since:0.3.0">
<title>gdict_defbox_set_font_name ()</title>
<indexterm zone="gdict-defbox-set-font-name" role="0.3.0"><primary sortas="gdict_defbox_set_font_name">gdict_defbox_set_font_name</primary></indexterm><programlisting><link linkend="void">void</link>                gdict_defbox_set_font_name          (<link linkend="GdictDefbox">GdictDefbox</link> *defbox,
                                                         const <link linkend="gchar">gchar</link> *font_name);</programlisting>
<para>
Sets <parameter>font_name</parameter> as the font for <parameter>defbox</parameter>. It calls internally
<link linkend="pango-font-description-from-string"><function>pango_font_description_from_string()</function></link> and <link linkend="gtk-widget-modify-font"><function>gtk_widget_modify_font()</function></link>.
</para>
<para>
Passing <link linkend="NULL--CAPS"><literal>NULL</literal></link> for <parameter>font_name</parameter> will reset any previously set font.</para>
<para>
</para><variablelist role="params">
<varlistentry><term><parameter>defbox</parameter>&#160;:</term>
<listitem><simpara> a <link linkend="GdictDefbox"><type>GdictDefbox</type></link>
</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
<varlistentry><term><parameter>font_name</parameter>&#160;:</term>
<listitem><simpara> a font description, or <link linkend="NULL--CAPS"><literal>NULL</literal></link>
</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
</variablelist><para role="since">Since 0.3.0</para></refsect2>
