<para>
Retrieves the font currently used by <parameter>defbox</parameter>.</para>
<para>
</para><variablelist role="params">
<varlistentry><term><parameter>defbox</parameter>&#160;:</term>
<listitem><simpara> a <link linkend="GdictDefbox"><type>GdictDefbox</type></link>
</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
<varlistentry><term><emphasis>Returns</emphasis>&#160;:</term><listitem><simpara> a font name.  The returned string is owned by <parameter>defbox</parameter> and
  should not be modified or freed.

</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
</variablelist><para role="since">Since 0.3</para></refsect2>
